### Product Service API Tests

@host = http://localhost:8082/api/v1/products
@token = Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Verificar Salud (Health Check)
GET {{host}}/status

### 2. Crear un Producto (Create Product)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "KB-MECH-RGB",
  "name": "Teclado Mecanico RGB",
  "description": "Switch Brown, Layout Espanol",
  "price": 89.99,
  "stock": 15
}

### 3. Obtener Producto por SKU (Get by SKU) - NEW 2026
GET {{host}}/sku/KB-MECH-RGB
Authorization: {{token}}

### 4. Listar Productos (List Products)
GET {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. Crear otro Producto (Create Another Product)
POST {{host}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "MOUSE-WL-20K",
  "name": "Mouse Gamer Wireless",
  "description": "20000 DPI, 7 Botones",
  "price": 59.50,
  "stock": 50
}

### 6. Probar Error 404 (RFC 7807)
GET {{host}}/sku/NON-EXISTENT-SKU
Authorization: {{token}}
